<title>UK: Daily Mail completes Southex purchase.</title>
<headline>Daily Mail completes Southex purchase.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-10-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Daily Mail &amp; General Trust Plc said on Monday it has completed the purchase of Southex Exhibitions from Canadian media group Southam Inc for 36.2 million stg in cash.</p>
<p>It said the investment in Southex was highly complementary to that of its unit DMG Exhibition Group Ltd, which is responsible for home and lifestyle exhibitions in the UK.</p>
<p>The Daily Mail Group has interests in newspapers, periodicals, broadcasting, conferences, video and book publishing as well as DMG Exhibition.</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 4019</p>
